wdi2-SH.XPD.GHED.GE.ZS.def: Public expenditure on health from domestic sources as a share of total public expenditure.  It indicates the priority of the government to spend on health from own domestic public resources.
wdi2-SH.XPD.GHED.GE.ZS.name: Domestic general government health expenditure
wdi2-SH.XPD.GHED.GE.ZS.source: World Health Organization Global Health Expenditure database (http://apps.who.int/nha/database).
